::Scattershot/Reptilica/Bloodystrike/Oblitercons::

Reptilica, Bloodystrike, Scattershot, Scavanger, Breakdown, and Hiss steps 
back from the Alliance ship, looking proudly at the job they had done fixing 
the hole. Not only was it fixed, but now reinforced.

Reptilica frowns as he sees objects on the ship. On a closer inspection, they 
prove to be explosives.

"Scanners," he yells into his wrist, "Scan all frequences!!"

The report comes up on his optics. There were some fady signatures around. 
"Everyone, search the area!"

With that order, the six outside took out their guns, on alert for the 
signatures around (Arcangel, Shocker, and IceDragon).
